snippet.title: Note Ban: Mamata Banerjee Joins Protest at Jantar Mantar in Delhi

localized.description:
Demonetisation: West Bengal Chief Minister Mamata Banerjee with her TMC workers join the protest at Jantar Mantar in Delhi against Modi government over demonetisation of Rs 500 and Rs 1000 notes.
